node.text:
Ok so....on today's ep of King & BJs Home Decor & Renovation. This is our OLD bathroom. When we started putting the final touches on the closet
(see yesterday's post) I looked at the bathroom & said..."Nahhhh now you know I can't walk through this old ass bathroom into this illustrious haberdashery...BJ we gotta run through this muuuufucka too!!!" So we did. But when we started I said "We can't do no normal shit tho... it's gotta be the dopest shit you ever done." That's when we went to work. Shit took me over budget tremendously cause we had to tear out the first tile since it didn't give Me what I was looking for (domestic junk wasn't givin what it was supposed to be givin- @kamayadaplug voice). That's when we went with the Italian imported Gold Calacatta 24'x24' heated marble. Tub-in-Shower 
(perfect for entertaining😇) equipped with automated controls and imported back lit onyx slabs (never done before in a shower😉) 50'smart TV swivels off the wall so wherever u at in there you can get a good view. Now this is around the time I started to really enjoy the process but it's important to point out again...This the "Other"house & we just got Another house so....what y'all think gon be doper? 🤷🏽‍♂️ Me & @themoderncraftsman placing bets. Just watch what we got goin on at THE BLACK HOUSE😈🤯🥶🔜💥👑
